Baillie ‘Extremely Concerned’ by Olympus Management Changes

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-10-21T15:24:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/baillie-extremely-concerned-by-olympus-management-changes.html
Baillie Gifford & Co. said it was
“extremely concerned” by unexpected management changes and
“allegations of financial impropriety” at  Olympus Corp. (7733) ,
according to an e-mailed statement today.  The Edinburgh-based investment management group invests in
Olympus Corp on behalf of some of its clients.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Rummer in London at 
